      "front": "I think I'm happy.",
      "back": "幸せだと思います。",
      "romanized": "Shiawase da to omoimasu.",
      "grammarNote": "For nouns and な-adjectives, add だ before と: 幸せだと思います.",
      "literal": "Happy is [quote] think."
    },
    {
      "id": "muzukashii_to_omoimasu",
      "front": "I think it's difficult.",
